Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}現在的你 全力支持著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在的我 也有了支持你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使彷徨無助 我們也要結伴前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}奔向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與朋友們嬉戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}這樣一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻依然感到內心的空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受盡冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}寄身於時代的狂風中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}勇氣與不安 如影相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}因此 現在就要用我的雙手創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}那些讓我們受傷感到絕望的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些令我們哭泣感到難過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然縈繞於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們終將跨過重重障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}以超越所有人為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}君が今僕を支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が今君を支える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから迷いながらも共に生きていこうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲間と戯れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}それなりで居ても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もの足りなさを感じてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷めた目で見られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}乾いた時代の風に吹かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}不安な心と勇気が背中合わせになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}だけど今なら夢をこの手で叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}傷ついて壊れそうな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙して困らせる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕達はそれを越えていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}誰より上を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:49.06,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經幻想 夢中的幸福{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:56.02,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人親手為我實現{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:03.08,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在繁忙的都市中尋找藉口{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:09.83,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們都在編織著美麗的謊言{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:17.39,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你這樣 真的滿足了嗎?」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:25.54,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在內心深處審視自己{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.26,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒能與你相遇{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.63,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會強顏歡笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.70,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著虛偽的面具度過{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.45,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你眼中的堅定{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.67,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我逐漸改變{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.53,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了擺脫昨日飄浮不定的心緒…{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:49.06,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に見ていたシアワセなら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:56.02,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが運んでくれると思ってた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:03.08,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急ぎ足の街で言い訳ばかり{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:09.83,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなも同じとうそぶいてた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:17.39,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「本当にキミはいま　満足してるの？」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:25.54,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の真ん中見抜かれたようで{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.26,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたと出会えなかったら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.63,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽った笑顔のまま{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.70,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うわべの態度や言葉を繰り返したね{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.45,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの瞳の力で{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.67,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私は変わってゆこう{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.53,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日の揺らいた気持ちを脱ぎ捨てるために…{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安時代的棋師 藤原佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越了遙遠的時空 在進藤光的心中復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了領悟「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\pos(440,380)}難忘之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要連勝好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為朝著目標全身心投入的人都在爭得你死我活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次老師的研究會還是在星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去了森田老師的研究會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然受益匪淺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還…還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我也該去參加個研究會了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是從早到晚都要下圍棋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的確也該偶爾出去散散心不然就累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 今天結束後去唱卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 太好了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再去打保齡球怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也叫上伊角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去給家裏打個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了 那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既不想去唱卡拉OK 也不想去打保齡球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有時很想回到圍棋社下下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下這裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時上完課不是馬上就回家的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是在家學圍棋吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 很認真地學習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼很認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是陪你沒完沒了的下棋罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事就先不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大賽怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生要參加吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽馬上要開始了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的退出了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我跟他說了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在和他不在同一班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒什麼機會和他說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是關於圍棋社的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果什麼時候他願意回來的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺圍棋社好像變得冷清了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我下一會兒棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總是陪不會下棋的女孩子一定也悶壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我跟你們1對3吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣? 怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不要再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才夏目也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷說不定過不了多久就想回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果偷偷來這裏的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發現小光在這裏下得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷肯定會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就再也不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就這一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一次沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去拿個棋盤來 我要下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想放幾個子就放幾個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我真的不客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些就夠了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就這些?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經擺了這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(415,146)}{\c&H000000&\bord0\fnsimhei\fs15\fr-1}\N化\N學\N實\N驗\N室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小光贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明放了那麼多子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 棋子都被提走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點也不手下留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都被你打得很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾我也要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…三谷!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光他只是碰巧今天過來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有埋怨進藤什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是忘記拿化學筆記本 回來拿罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 明天來拿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓院生大人來教你們真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼忘記拿筆記本 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在靠窗那排最裏面的那張桌子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷說忘記拿化學筆記本 只是過來拿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今天應該沒有化學課
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天玉子老師請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}小光是白癡!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 小明!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷不會再來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 快點收拾好棋子回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 下次不會再來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 住手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs25\bord0\c&H000000&\pos(123,273)\b1\fad(200,0)}耐\N心\N指\N導
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs25\bord0\c&H000000&\b1\pos(325,56)\fad(200,0)} 召集圍棋社會員!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs25\bord0\c&H000000&\b1\pos(517,314)\fad(200,0)}初\N學\N者\N也\N可\N以\N放\N心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs25\bord0\c&H000000&\b1\pos(325,469)\fad(200,0)}放學後在化學實驗室下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是一年前的這個時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤把我硬拉進了圍棋社
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海報已經貼出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒人來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷也沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再重新做一張海報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年也是重新做了海報 才把三谷吸引過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼女生為了下個月的大賽先做下特訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 我們真的要參賽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我已經拜託排球社的金子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上津田 一共三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生就我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 我想參加圍棋社 可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問三谷在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是關於圍棋社的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋社?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在那裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪那兩個下得差勁的女生下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 她們兩個已經不是那麼差了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經下得有模有樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此 昨天還有新人加入了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個一年級的雖然不怎麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和我的水平差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 男生社員已經有兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你回來的話 就能參賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們的主將吧 三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課鈴響了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回自己教室去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後先別回去記得等我 我還會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 昨天的作業…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1810,0)\pos(415,146)}{\c&H000000&\bord0\fnsimhei\fs15\fr-1}\N化\N學\N實\N驗\N室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下來要做課本上第47頁的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家準備好要用的器材
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}讓我用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}不行 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}我會還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}啊 對了 那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}不需要那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}用那個就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}等等 怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}要小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}不是我啦 是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 那裏由老師來收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.80,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\pos(408,254)\fs20\fr-5}藤崎 明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽記錄?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始記這些東西了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了不少盤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共五本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 不是已經有5個社員了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會下棋的那個女生 還有夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小池仁志?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 夏目你就這樣放棄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天再去勸勸他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也再去說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}反正只要我們努力向前 就一定會有好結果的 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小池也加入了圍棋社
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是新海報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 已經做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想加上一道死活題來著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 做得很好 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你肯參加大賽了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你同意當主將了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼? 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不參加大賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你來這裏做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想偶爾來和我下幾盤棋?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再拿出一個棋盤來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先跟夏目和小池1對2來下盤棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一年級的小池
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再和我們下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他見識一下變強的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來練練手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也是參加比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該常來這裏好好地練習一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的人誰最厲害?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要抓子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真不客氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要和我分先下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你才第一次下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想知道實力高低當然應該分先下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我讓子的話請隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要給我讓子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你蠻有自信的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們快點開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我先下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你可不利啊 要不要貼目10目半?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要再讓三谷離開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒下了 都沒狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 金子的棋子順利地連上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 三谷知道自己現在佔上風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有特意封殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓對方連起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣 金子也比我和小池強多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪那麼有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多該認輸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了吧? 要說「我輸了」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是有些對手我是不想向他認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 沒辦法只能說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來讓我三子怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有本事贏我的話就讓你三子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種說話方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33}如果真的輸了的話\N會沒臉見人的所以還是不要這樣說比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們要把對局結果記下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷的對局終於可以順利地開始記錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直都是空白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種對局結果不要記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要準備一個金子的對局筆記本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記下來 記下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把我戰勝這傢伙的對局越來越多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受的讓子越來越少的成績都記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 金子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 金子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小光是同一班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能替我轉告他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說三谷已經回到圍棋社了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他放心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 但明天進藤請假了 星期一再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請假?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:20:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟老師說要參加什麼幼獅賽就請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也有自己的比賽要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再…再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天還是讓我三子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說我明天要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算你不戰而敗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼要讓你三子啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天讓了你三子 你不是輸得很慘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天也輸得很慘的話那就讓我四子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了 誰告訴你我明天還會來啊?
